{"title":"村姑","authors":["李业成"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":4,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"村姑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李业成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她常常对着这面大山发愁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山下的一条路走回来走回去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总也走不出山外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些开满儿时小竹篮的荠菜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又约来遍地小黄蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小溪依然没有长大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滑下青苔嬉戏着追远了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她长大了，溪头坐着发愁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不远的山外就有大海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但她从未到过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一本绿封面的书上，怅望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥远遥远的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她常想应当做些什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但双臂柔得像山边枕着风的绿蔓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动后，就变得冰冷沉思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在夜露下的思绪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜能憋出很多枝丫"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}